Form for any User (Athlete and/or Coach):
<ul>
<li>Full Name</li>
<li>Date of Birth (Drop down calendar)</li>
<li>Passport size photo (to be uploaded by the Athlete)</li>
<li>Address (Full Postal Address)</li>
<li>Gender (Male or Female)</li>
