Total Count of Male/Female Trainees
Total Count of Current Coaches
Total Count of Current Athletes
Outstanding athletes trained in the past
Strengths
Summary/Statement on the Academy’s success story
Action Photos and Videos (photos and video links of athletes training at the respective academy to be uploaded/provided by the Academy)
